room_title: Escape room "Baker Street Mystery" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: I've done two rooms here so far. We did bank heist with Ryan doing a wonderful job running it and Baker Street with Tyler, who was really helpful. I've done a lot of these rooms, and the staff and setup are always great. I would definitely recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Baker Street Mystery" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: We did the Baker Street escape room yesterday and had so much fun. This was their most challenging escape room, and we just barely escaped it at 59:07. The staff are very friendly and the set up of their escape rooms are so fun. Check it out!

room_title: Escape room "Baker Street Mystery" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: We celebrated a 17th birthday with 9 girls solving a mystery in the Baker Street room. Morgan was a great hostess, giving them the right amount assistance. Highly recommend!
